1
00:00:01,010 --> 00:00:03,850
<i>LOVE AND REDEMPTION</i>

2
00:00:04,400 --> 00:00:06,640
<i>EPISODE 5</i>

3
00:00:08,600 --> 00:00:11,039
Chu Ling Long and
Zhong Min Yan from Shaoyang Sect

4
00:00:11,040 --> 00:00:14,640
will fight Su Bo and Mo Shao Yan
from Dianjinggu Sect.

5
00:00:16,840 --> 00:00:18,679
Ling Long, it’s our turn.

6
00:00:18,680 --> 00:00:20,507
Xuan Ji, you must cheer for me.

7
00:00:20,508 --> 00:00:21,679
Ling Long, you must do your best.

8
00:00:21,680 --> 00:00:23,439
Sixth Senior, you too.

9
00:00:23,440 --> 00:00:25,000
Let’s go, Little Six.

10
00:00:28,360 --> 00:00:30,280
Ling Long. Be careful!

11
00:01:11,080 --> 00:01:12,320
Ling Long!

12
00:01:23,240 --> 00:01:24,400
Ling Long!

13
00:01:26,240 --> 00:01:27,480
Ling Long!

14
00:01:30,680 --> 00:01:32,519
Are you alright?

15
00:01:32,520 --> 00:01:37,479
I’m fine but I
lost just like that.

16
00:01:37,480 --> 00:01:40,039
Don’t cry. Ling Long.

17
00:01:40,040 --> 00:01:42,639
It’s alright. We still have Sixth Senior.

18
00:01:42,640 --> 00:01:44,759
Shaoyang Sect will win
if Sixth Senior wins.

19
00:01:44,760 --> 00:01:46,760
Do your best! Sixth Senior!

20
00:01:47,480 --> 00:01:49,719
Little Six, you have to do your best.

21
00:01:49,720 --> 00:01:51,679
Get revenge for me.
Little Six, do your best!

22
00:01:51,680 --> 00:01:54,277
I said it. Shaoyang Sect is full of trash.

23
00:01:54,278 --> 00:01:55,599
I was right.

24
00:01:55,600 --> 00:01:58,200
Are you looking for a fight?
You are the trash.

25
00:01:59,040 --> 00:02:02,118
Miss Ling Long, you were just
crying when you fell off the stage.

26
00:02:02,119 --> 00:02:03,654
Are you acting tough now?

27
00:02:03,655 --> 00:02:05,799
What’s wrong? Want a fight?

28
00:02:05,800 --> 00:02:08,474
- Let’s do it!
- You talk big.

29
00:02:08,475 --> 00:02:10,959
Unfortunately, out of the two daughters
of Shaoyang Sect,

30
00:02:10,960 --> 00:02:13,919
one of them lost to the disciples
of Dianjinggu Sect

31
00:02:13,920 --> 00:02:15,079
- While the other one...
- What are you talking about?

32
00:02:15,080 --> 00:02:16,974
She is a trash who doesn’t
even know martial arts.

33
00:02:16,975 --> 00:02:17,999
How can you fight me?

34
00:02:18,000 --> 00:02:19,862
I’ll kill you for
talking bad about my sister!

35
00:02:19,863 --> 00:02:21,223
Ling Long.

36
00:02:21,960 --> 00:02:23,999
Don’t talk to him. He is a bad guy.

37
00:02:24,000 --> 00:02:25,559
Shaoyang Sect will not lose.

38
00:02:25,560 --> 00:02:27,168
Sixth Senior, keep it up!

39
00:02:27,169 --> 00:02:28,493
Little Six, keep it up!

40
00:02:28,494 --> 00:02:29,559
Defeat him!

41
00:02:29,560 --> 00:02:30,840
Do you best!

42
00:02:43,640 --> 00:02:45,600
- Little Six, keep it up!
- Keep it up!

43
00:02:46,280 --> 00:02:47,926
Sixth Senior, keep it up!

44
00:02:47,927 --> 00:02:49,360
Little Six!

45
00:02:53,360 --> 00:02:55,755
Zhong Min Yan from Shaoyang Sect wins.

46
00:02:56,584 --> 00:02:57,779
We won!

47
00:02:59,280 --> 00:03:01,039
Little Six won!

48
00:03:01,040 --> 00:03:03,519
- Shaoyang Sect won!
- You made me proud!

49
00:03:03,520 --> 00:03:05,400
Little Six is great!

50
00:03:14,400 --> 00:03:15,829
My lord.

51
00:03:15,830 --> 00:03:17,239
What’s wrong?

52
00:03:17,240 --> 00:03:19,759
You know the whereabouts
of the spirit keys?

53
00:03:19,760 --> 00:03:21,198
My lord.

54
00:03:21,199 --> 00:03:22,639
The spirit keys are important.

55
00:03:22,640 --> 00:03:24,598
Only those who are above the rank
of elders among the Five Great Sect

56
00:03:24,599 --> 00:03:26,239
know about their whereabouts.

57
00:03:26,240 --> 00:03:28,719
Please give me more time.

58
00:03:28,720 --> 00:03:30,630
Let me give you a hint.

59
00:03:30,631 --> 00:03:33,278
Xuanyuan Sect used to be
the leader of the Five Great Sects.

60
00:03:33,279 --> 00:03:35,134
Now that they are at
the bottom of the pile,

61
00:03:35,135 --> 00:03:37,398
they must be bearing a grudge.

62
00:03:37,399 --> 00:03:40,740
This is your opportunity.

63
00:03:50,831 --> 00:03:52,599
Inside this bottle are Kunyin Pills.

64
00:03:52,600 --> 00:03:55,439
Take one and it will increase your power.

65
00:03:55,440 --> 00:03:58,574
If Xuanyuan Sect
wants to impress at the Flower session,

66
00:03:58,575 --> 00:04:00,399
they will need these pills.

67
00:04:00,400 --> 00:04:04,838
As long as they take one of
the pills, they will definitely spill

68
00:04:04,839 --> 00:04:07,480
the secrets of
the spirit keys of Five Great Sect.

69
00:04:08,360 --> 00:04:10,039
What a brilliant idea.

70
00:04:10,040 --> 00:04:11,600
You enlightened me.

71
00:04:15,039 --> 00:04:18,039
Our sword moves and styles
are related to your inner force.

72
00:04:18,040 --> 00:04:19,717
I don’t mind
if your inner force isn’t strong

73
00:04:19,718 --> 00:04:21,439
but your moves were rusty as well.

74
00:04:21,440 --> 00:04:23,280
Master, I was wrong.

75
00:04:24,040 --> 00:04:26,334
You lost badly in the first match.

76
00:04:26,335 --> 00:04:28,399
You embarrassed me.

77
00:04:28,400 --> 00:04:29,574
Shi Feng.

78
00:04:30,360 --> 00:04:31,999
You will fight tomorrow.

79
00:04:32,000 --> 00:04:35,160
If you dare lose again,
I will not forgive you.

80
00:04:35,920 --> 00:04:39,000
I will do my best to
make Master proud.

81
00:04:40,760 --> 00:04:42,517
Both your trainings are not enough

82
00:04:42,518 --> 00:04:44,799
yet you were ordered
to participate in the Flower Session.

83
00:04:44,800 --> 00:04:46,246
I know it’s hard for both of you.

84
00:04:46,247 --> 00:04:48,079
Leave.

85
00:04:48,080 --> 00:04:49,640
- Yes.
- Yes.

86
00:05:06,720 --> 00:05:10,160
I am pleased to meet you, Elder Ling Shi.

87
00:05:11,480 --> 00:05:13,239
Who are you?

88
00:05:13,240 --> 00:05:16,039
I’m just a nameless person
who knows that Xuanyuan Sect

89
00:05:16,040 --> 00:05:18,680
has been facing unexpected changes lately.

90
00:05:20,200 --> 00:05:22,774
Xuanyuan Sect is
the leader of the Five Great Sect.

91
00:05:22,775 --> 00:05:25,200
There are no changes at all.

92
00:05:25,880 --> 00:05:28,279
Xuanyuan Sect has been
making forbidden medicines

93
00:05:28,280 --> 00:05:29,959
in hopes of increasing power.

94
00:05:29,960 --> 00:05:31,231
Unexpectedly,

95
00:05:31,232 --> 00:05:34,359
the forbidden medicine caused a few
of your disciples to die suddenly.

96
00:05:34,360 --> 00:05:40,238
The sect leader almost went mad,
and even had to hide in the secret room.

97
00:05:40,239 --> 00:05:42,799
Fortunately, Elder Ling Shi, you
didn’t take much of the medicine.

98
00:05:42,800 --> 00:05:45,182
To avoid being
found out by the other sects,

99
00:05:45,183 --> 00:05:47,766
you had to choose some average disciples

100
00:05:47,767 --> 00:05:51,199
to participate
in this Flower Session with you.

101
00:05:51,200 --> 00:05:55,359
Does this count as an unexpected change?

102
00:05:55,360 --> 00:05:58,182
- You...
- You don’t have to panic.

103
00:05:58,183 --> 00:06:00,980
I’m just trying
to help with your concerns.

104
00:06:01,840 --> 00:06:06,502
I just added a secret medicine
of the demon clan in your tea.

105
00:06:06,503 --> 00:06:08,199
Kunyin Pill.

106
00:06:08,200 --> 00:06:09,502
You are from the demon clan?

107
00:06:09,503 --> 00:06:12,439
I’m also your friend.

108
00:06:12,440 --> 00:06:15,319
Kunyin Pill can increase your inner force.

109
00:06:15,320 --> 00:06:19,959
I’m sure Xuanyuan Sect will become
the champion of this Flower Session.

110
00:06:19,960 --> 00:06:22,246
This is a rare opportunity.

111
00:06:22,247 --> 00:06:25,239
It is very important
to you and Xuanyuan Sect.

112
00:06:25,240 --> 00:06:30,000
If you don’t believe me, you
can try out your own power.

113
00:06:50,800 --> 00:06:54,079
Are you hunting
in the middle of the night?

114
00:06:54,080 --> 00:06:55,319
Si Feng.

115
00:06:55,320 --> 00:06:57,200
I’m practising my sword.

116
00:07:01,320 --> 00:07:03,679
You are practising
because you were laughed at

117
00:07:03,680 --> 00:07:05,479
by the people of Dianjinggu Sect?

118
00:07:05,480 --> 00:07:06,760
I...

119
00:07:08,000 --> 00:07:10,279
I don’t want to be a burden.

120
00:07:10,280 --> 00:07:14,359
But perhaps I was born
without the six senses,

121
00:07:14,360 --> 00:07:16,653
so I can’t master it even though
I’ve practised for the whole night.

122
00:07:16,654 --> 00:07:18,280
Show me.

123
00:07:22,800 --> 00:07:24,959
Hold with pity.

124
00:07:26,040 --> 00:07:28,079
Strike with compassion!

125
00:07:28,080 --> 00:07:30,160
See. Isn’t it hard?

126
00:07:30,775 --> 00:07:31,999
Basic technique?

127
00:07:32,000 --> 00:07:34,149
Si Feng, you are so smart.
You guessed it straight away.

128
00:07:34,150 --> 00:07:38,319
Hold with pity means
to judge the situation before you act.

129
00:07:38,320 --> 00:07:39,813
Strike with compassion means

130
00:07:39,814 --> 00:07:43,230
leave a gap after you strike
to be flexible for unexpected situations.

131
00:07:43,231 --> 00:07:46,757
Now that you have a sense of
taste, you can feel it with that.

132
00:07:46,758 --> 00:07:49,319
For example, you are fighting for food.

133
00:07:49,320 --> 00:07:51,590
You can choose your favourite food

134
00:07:51,591 --> 00:07:55,461
and calculate
your power, speed and distance

135
00:07:55,462 --> 00:07:56,878
to make sure that you get it.

136
00:07:56,879 --> 00:07:58,687
This is hold with pity.

137
00:07:58,688 --> 00:08:02,512
Strike with compassion means
looking at food at the table while eating

138
00:08:02,513 --> 00:08:05,159
and think about how to get the food later?

139
00:08:05,160 --> 00:08:06,639
I guess so.

140
00:08:06,640 --> 00:08:11,005
By the way, your understanding
do increase once it’s about food.

141
00:08:11,006 --> 00:08:12,840
Practise again.

142
00:08:19,841 --> 00:08:21,720
Hold with pity.

143
00:08:37,600 --> 00:08:38,880
Si Feng!

144
00:08:40,598 --> 00:08:43,440
I didn’t expect the power to be so strong.

145
00:08:44,095 --> 00:08:46,079
It’s just a basic technique.

146
00:08:46,080 --> 00:08:48,599
But this way of thinking suits you.

147
00:08:48,600 --> 00:08:51,159
Just keep practising like this later on.

148
00:08:51,160 --> 00:08:54,879
But... But your
purse is damaged.

149
00:08:54,880 --> 00:08:56,120
It’s fine.

150
00:08:57,695 --> 00:08:58,999
Wrap it with this.

151
00:08:59,000 --> 00:09:02,200
Ling Long said the accessory
will get dirty if you are holding it.

152
00:09:06,840 --> 00:09:10,718
This is passed down from my mum.
I can’t dirty it indeed.

153
00:09:10,719 --> 00:09:13,126
I will accept your handkerchief for now.

154
00:09:13,127 --> 00:09:14,320
Thank you.

155
00:09:15,600 --> 00:09:17,039
Si Feng.

156
00:09:17,040 --> 00:09:20,742
Your mother must be nice to you.

157
00:09:20,743 --> 00:09:24,800
Otherwise, you won’t
treasure the things she left you.

158
00:09:25,910 --> 00:09:27,440
I grew up in Lize Palace

159
00:09:28,000 --> 00:09:29,800
since I was young.

160
00:09:30,480 --> 00:09:32,600
I’ve never met my parents before.

161
00:09:33,320 --> 00:09:35,360
But the only thing they left me

162
00:09:36,000 --> 00:09:40,080
is this golden hairpin and
a portrait of my mother.

163
00:09:42,503 --> 00:09:43,759
Si Feng.

164
00:09:43,760 --> 00:09:45,480
Was your mother pretty?

165
00:09:47,360 --> 00:09:51,519
Although I have no way
of explaining what is pretty to you,

166
00:09:51,520 --> 00:09:54,279
my mother was very pretty indeed.

167
00:09:54,280 --> 00:09:57,279
Your mother should be very pretty too.

168
00:09:57,280 --> 00:09:58,600
Which is why

169
00:09:59,200 --> 00:10:01,400
you are so pretty as well.

170
00:10:02,720 --> 00:10:04,200
But

171
00:10:04,760 --> 00:10:09,839
my mother left me
when I was very young too.

172
00:10:09,840 --> 00:10:14,839
I remember she had always cared
and protected me when I was young.

173
00:10:14,840 --> 00:10:20,398
But when she passed
away, I couldn’t even cry.

174
00:10:20,399 --> 00:10:22,158
I wished I have the six senses.

175
00:10:22,159 --> 00:10:25,920
I will be able to cry just like Ling Long.

176
00:10:28,320 --> 00:10:30,639
Xuan Ji, don’t worry.

177
00:10:30,640 --> 00:10:34,558
I will find the glass shards for
you to restore your six senses.

178
00:10:34,559 --> 00:10:35,799
Really?

179
00:10:35,800 --> 00:10:38,039
It’s a promise.

180
00:10:38,040 --> 00:10:40,199
Let’s leave our sects and
go on an adventure four years later.

181
00:10:40,200 --> 00:10:41,440
Alright?

182
00:10:44,640 --> 00:10:45,879
It’s your saliva again.

183
00:10:45,880 --> 00:10:49,253
Ling Long said
this is the strongest form of promise.

184
00:10:49,254 --> 00:10:51,239
You will not break your promise.

185
00:10:51,240 --> 00:10:52,880
You are childish.

186
00:11:18,920 --> 00:11:21,480
Shi Feng from Xuanyuan Sect wins.

187
00:11:25,943 --> 00:11:28,894
Shi Feng is strong.

188
00:11:28,895 --> 00:11:31,643
He looks handsome too.

189
00:11:34,407 --> 00:11:36,119
Why haven’t I heard of

190
00:11:36,120 --> 00:11:38,700
a disciple with
strong inner force in Xuanyuan Sect?

191
00:11:42,791 --> 00:11:45,399
You were winning every match yesterday.

192
00:11:45,400 --> 00:11:46,999
Impressive.

193
00:11:47,000 --> 00:11:50,406
You made Xuanyuan Sect proud.

194
00:11:50,407 --> 00:11:51,639
Not bad.

195
00:11:51,640 --> 00:11:54,382
The qi inside me is increasing.

196
00:11:54,383 --> 00:11:55,800
I can’t control it.

197
00:11:56,534 --> 00:11:57,838
Master.

198
00:11:57,839 --> 00:12:02,359
The pill that you gave me.
Do you think it’s... Shut up.

199
00:12:02,360 --> 00:12:06,839
The pill that I gave you
will only strengthen you.

200
00:12:06,840 --> 00:12:08,439
You don’t have to worry.

201
00:12:08,440 --> 00:12:13,000
Master, I’m worried that I will end up
like my seniors and juniors.

202
00:12:13,527 --> 00:12:16,599
- Dying from excessive qi.
- That’s impossible.

203
00:12:16,600 --> 00:12:18,799
They took forbidden medicines.

204
00:12:18,800 --> 00:12:22,261
What I gave you were pills made by myself.

205
00:12:22,262 --> 00:12:24,000
How could you compare them?

206
00:12:32,000 --> 00:12:33,559
Feng Er.

207
00:12:33,560 --> 00:12:37,446
What I’m always doing is for
the good of Xuanyuan Sect.

208
00:12:37,447 --> 00:12:40,799
Don’t you trust your master anymore?

209
00:12:40,800 --> 00:12:42,334
No.

210
00:12:42,335 --> 00:12:44,160
That’s good.

211
00:12:45,264 --> 00:12:47,239
You worked hard today.

212
00:12:47,240 --> 00:12:49,000
Go back to rest.

213
00:12:49,800 --> 00:12:51,400
Yes, Master.

214
00:12:54,680 --> 00:12:55,943
Wait.

215
00:12:56,920 --> 00:13:01,720
Remember. Don’t tell
anyone about this pill.

216
00:13:02,240 --> 00:13:03,479
Yes.

217
00:13:03,480 --> 00:13:04,760
Go back.

218
00:13:12,440 --> 00:13:14,214
Congratulations, elder.

219
00:13:14,215 --> 00:13:17,270
Congratulations, Xuanyuan
Sect, for the consecutive victory

220
00:13:17,271 --> 00:13:18,742
and impressive performances.

221
00:13:18,743 --> 00:13:20,143
Tell me.

222
00:13:20,144 --> 00:13:21,904
What do you want?

223
00:13:21,905 --> 00:13:26,086
I’m just hoping that you can
provide me with some information.

224
00:13:26,087 --> 00:13:27,493
What is it?

225
00:13:27,494 --> 00:13:30,520
The whereabouts of the four spirit keys.

226
00:13:46,400 --> 00:13:48,160
Keep it up! Sixth Senior!

227
00:13:52,080 --> 00:13:53,687
Despicable! You used a hidden weapon.

228
00:13:53,688 --> 00:13:55,389
Despicable!

229
00:14:03,400 --> 00:14:04,640
Little Six!

230
00:14:14,680 --> 00:14:16,560
- Little Six!
- Sixth Senior!

231
00:14:39,680 --> 00:14:40,960
Xuan Ji!

232
00:14:41,480 --> 00:14:43,600
Xuan Ji, are you alright?

233
00:14:46,800 --> 00:14:48,439
Wu Tong, you are so despicable!

234
00:14:48,440 --> 00:14:51,614
You used a hidden weapon and
a forbidden skill when you are losing.

235
00:14:51,615 --> 00:14:53,431
Do you know you almost hurt my sister?

236
00:14:53,432 --> 00:14:55,405
You should be banned from the tournament.

237
00:14:55,406 --> 00:14:57,200
Yes, you should be banned!

238
00:14:58,111 --> 00:14:59,829
Flower Session is
a place to show our skills.

239
00:14:59,830 --> 00:15:01,399
When did spells become a forbidden skill?

240
00:15:01,400 --> 00:15:03,958
There are many spectators.
Only your sister failed to dodge it.

241
00:15:03,959 --> 00:15:05,736
That’s because she’s stupid.
It’s none of my business.

242
00:15:05,737 --> 00:15:07,720
- You...
- He is right.

243
00:15:09,168 --> 00:15:12,399
Spell is a permitted technique.

244
00:15:12,400 --> 00:15:13,999
It’s just that participants from
previous Flower Sessions

245
00:15:14,000 --> 00:15:17,639
were not as highly skilled and
not many of them can use it.

246
00:15:17,640 --> 00:15:21,566
What’s wrong? Our disciple, Wu Tong,
is just hardworking

247
00:15:21,567 --> 00:15:25,119
and has a better cultivation
yet he is the one at fault?

248
00:15:25,120 --> 00:15:28,799
But his spell almost
get someone else hurt.

249
00:15:28,800 --> 00:15:31,427
Spells have a high range.

250
00:15:31,428 --> 00:15:35,239
Shaoyang Sect didn’t do the necessary
safety precautions as the host

251
00:15:35,240 --> 00:15:37,318
and blames the participants?

252
00:15:37,319 --> 00:15:40,934
Unless, since the one
who lost is your disciple

253
00:15:40,935 --> 00:15:43,719
and the one who couldn’t
dodge the spell is your daughter,

254
00:15:43,720 --> 00:15:47,760
you felt embarrassed,
and try to put the blame on me?

255
00:15:49,160 --> 00:15:51,303
Valley Master Rong is right.

256
00:15:51,304 --> 00:15:53,159
It’s Shaoyang Sect’s negligence.

257
00:15:53,160 --> 00:15:56,240
This match is won by Wu Tong.

258
00:15:58,840 --> 00:16:02,920
As such, I thank Sect Leader Zhu
for your fair judgement.

259
00:16:03,703 --> 00:16:07,982
However, the spell is too powerful,
and hard to control.

260
00:16:07,983 --> 00:16:09,519
I’ll let it go this time.

261
00:16:09,520 --> 00:16:14,760
In the next match, every participant
is not allowed to use spells.

262
00:16:23,320 --> 00:16:24,759
I can’t stand it anymore!

263
00:16:24,760 --> 00:16:28,559
I have to kill Wu Tong to get
revenge for you and Xuan Ji.

264
00:16:28,560 --> 00:16:30,559
No. Don’t be rash.

265
00:16:30,560 --> 00:16:32,454
Wu Tong’s martial arts
and spells are not bad.

266
00:16:32,455 --> 00:16:34,079
Furthermore, he is ruthless.

267
00:16:34,080 --> 00:16:36,414
You might end up
getting embarrassed instead.

268
00:16:36,415 --> 00:16:38,518
I almost got beat up by him too.

269
00:16:38,519 --> 00:16:40,639
You are trying to say
that I’ve embarrassed myself, right?

270
00:16:40,640 --> 00:16:42,479
- This...
- I will not take this lying down.

271
00:16:42,480 --> 00:16:44,639
- Ask Xuan Ji if you don’t believe me.
- I...

272
00:16:44,640 --> 00:16:46,598
I think Wu Tong
is simply using his spells.

273
00:16:46,599 --> 00:16:48,270
Although it’s fine
for me because I feel no pain,

274
00:16:48,271 --> 00:16:50,719
he almost hurt Sixth Senior,
and everyone else.

275
00:16:50,720 --> 00:16:52,039
We have to get revenge.

276
00:16:52,040 --> 00:16:54,399
See? Even Xuan Ji can’t stand him.

277
00:16:54,400 --> 00:16:57,606
Wu Tong almost hurt Xuan Ji and Min Yan.

278
00:16:57,607 --> 00:17:00,758
Looks like we have to
give him some punishment.

279
00:17:00,759 --> 00:17:04,000
Brother, do you have an idea already?

280
00:17:07,480 --> 00:17:12,719
Lize Palace’s disciple, Yu Si
Feng, lost a silver spirit snake.

281
00:17:12,720 --> 00:17:17,079
Anyone who finds it will be
rewarded with ten luminous pearls.

282
00:17:17,080 --> 00:17:18,759
- Ten luminous pearls?
- Ten?

283
00:17:18,760 --> 00:17:20,439
Lize Palace’s people is rich.

284
00:17:20,440 --> 00:17:21,879
It’s so awesome.

285
00:17:21,880 --> 00:17:24,079
Silver spirit snake?

286
00:17:24,080 --> 00:17:26,119
Ten luminous pearls.
Let’s go and find it.

287
00:17:26,120 --> 00:17:28,132
Maybe we will be lucky.

288
00:17:28,133 --> 00:17:31,100
- Yes. Let’s go.
- You are right. Let’s go.

289
00:17:41,320 --> 00:17:43,542
Do you think he won’t come?

290
00:17:43,543 --> 00:17:47,279
Perhaps the reward is not enough?

291
00:17:47,280 --> 00:17:48,999
I’ve investigated it.

292
00:17:49,000 --> 00:17:50,479
Wu Tong was born in a poor family.

293
00:17:50,480 --> 00:17:54,439
He is thrifty, and practises hard
to gain fame.

294
00:17:54,440 --> 00:17:57,440
His match with Min Yan yesterday
exceeded his expectations.

295
00:17:58,008 --> 00:18:01,279
He had to use his secret weapon,
the spell.

296
00:18:01,280 --> 00:18:03,640
Now, his inner force is weakened.

297
00:18:04,519 --> 00:18:08,158
He needs money to buy the pills
to recover his inner force

298
00:18:08,159 --> 00:18:10,462
- so he can fight again.
- With that said,

299
00:18:10,463 --> 00:18:12,760
he will have to come
for this ten luminous pearls.

300
00:18:14,480 --> 00:18:15,760
He’s here.

301
00:18:49,280 --> 00:18:50,520
Don’t move.

302
00:19:16,920 --> 00:19:18,799
We’ve succeeded. Great!

303
00:19:18,800 --> 00:19:21,719
Si Feng, you are so great.
You calculated everything correctly.

304
00:19:21,720 --> 00:19:23,638
It’s easy to know
what Wu Tong is thinking.

305
00:19:23,639 --> 00:19:26,320
What are you thinking every day?

306
00:19:28,440 --> 00:19:30,230
Who is it? Come out!

307
00:19:30,231 --> 00:19:31,760
It’s us.

308
00:19:36,879 --> 00:19:39,239
You’re being arrogant.
You’re wrapped like a dumpling now.

309
00:19:39,240 --> 00:19:40,759
Do you know how great we are now?

310
00:19:40,760 --> 00:19:42,599
Shaoyang Sect
only knows these petty tricks.

311
00:19:42,600 --> 00:19:45,679
These petty tricks are used by scoundrels.

312
00:19:45,680 --> 00:19:48,319
You don’t have to care about that.
I caught you anyway.

313
00:19:48,320 --> 00:19:50,840
Apologise to my sister and senior. Hurry.

314
00:19:51,520 --> 00:19:54,719
Let me go! I’ve prepared
for four years for this Flower Session.

315
00:19:54,720 --> 00:19:57,081
I won’t forgive you
if you interfere with my match.

316
00:19:57,082 --> 00:19:58,999
How dare you complain as a captive.

317
00:19:59,000 --> 00:20:00,479
Fine. Don’t apologise.

318
00:20:00,480 --> 00:20:02,478
I will have you
trapped here for three whole days.

319
00:20:02,479 --> 00:20:03,877
Let’s go, Little Six.

320
00:20:03,878 --> 00:20:05,280
Wait!

321
00:20:07,760 --> 00:20:09,999
Fine. I will apologise.

322
00:20:10,000 --> 00:20:11,680
At least you’re still tactful.

323
00:20:16,400 --> 00:20:17,520
Look out!

324
00:20:23,560 --> 00:20:25,520
Ling Long! Are you alright?

325
00:20:26,471 --> 00:20:27,999
You are really cruel!

326
00:20:28,000 --> 00:20:30,702
If you hit Ling Long, she will die!

327
00:20:30,703 --> 00:20:32,559
How dare she ruin my future.

328
00:20:32,560 --> 00:20:33,782
I want to take her life indeed.

329
00:20:33,783 --> 00:20:37,206
I will definitely put a hole
in a bad guy like you!

330
00:20:37,207 --> 00:20:39,039
Don’t. He is tricky.

331
00:20:39,040 --> 00:20:42,559
You shouldn’t go near.
We only try to punish him today.

332
00:20:42,560 --> 00:20:46,200
If someone got hurt,
it’s hard to explain to the elders.

333
00:20:47,240 --> 00:20:51,519
Today, you will repent
here as punishment.

334
00:20:51,520 --> 00:20:53,158
My friend from Lize Palace.

335
00:20:53,159 --> 00:20:55,038
The match tomorrow is important for me.

336
00:20:55,039 --> 00:20:57,559
- Please let me down.
- No.

337
00:20:57,560 --> 00:20:59,799
We’ve finally set up a trap to catch you.

338
00:20:59,800 --> 00:21:01,559
Why should we let you go that easily?

339
00:21:01,560 --> 00:21:03,599
It was your idea?

340
00:21:03,600 --> 00:21:05,200
It’s just a random idea.

341
00:21:07,120 --> 00:21:09,799
I have many gold leaves here.
I’ll give them to you if you release me.

342
00:21:09,800 --> 00:21:11,519
People from Lize Palace don’t lack money.

343
00:21:11,520 --> 00:21:12,760
Please excuse us.

344
00:21:13,320 --> 00:21:14,999
Wait!

345
00:21:15,000 --> 00:21:16,302
Yu Si Feng!

346
00:21:16,303 --> 00:21:18,119
I will never forgive you!

347
00:21:18,120 --> 00:21:21,679
Just stay here and
calm yourself down.

348
00:21:21,680 --> 00:21:24,960
You can talk
when you return to Shaoyang Sect.

349
00:21:26,790 --> 00:21:27,845
Yu Si Feng!

350
00:21:27,846 --> 00:21:28,880
Let’s go.

351
00:21:34,600 --> 00:21:37,398
Si Feng, you have wonderful foresight.
You predicted everything.

352
00:21:37,399 --> 00:21:41,278
Tonight, Wu Tong will definitely
be bitten to death by bugs,

353
00:21:41,279 --> 00:21:43,720
froze to death,
and scared to death by ghosts.

354
00:21:44,320 --> 00:21:47,559
What happened was due to my weakness.

355
00:21:47,560 --> 00:21:51,480
I’ve decided to practise more from now on.

356
00:21:52,400 --> 00:21:56,519
I might not get to
join the next Flower Session,

357
00:21:56,520 --> 00:21:59,200
but at least I won’t be struck by a spell.

358
00:22:01,120 --> 00:22:02,480
Right?

359
00:22:15,200 --> 00:22:16,486
Look at you.

360
00:22:16,487 --> 00:22:18,039
With that ability,

361
00:22:18,040 --> 00:22:20,278
how can you become
the champion of the Flower Session?

362
00:22:20,279 --> 00:22:23,159
I will definitely work hard
or the next few days.

363
00:22:23,160 --> 00:22:25,239
It’s just that I feel my inner force
is not as great

364
00:22:25,240 --> 00:22:29,400
as the past few days so
my techniques are weaker.

365
00:22:30,280 --> 00:22:31,378
Master.

366
00:22:31,379 --> 00:22:34,600
Why don’t you give me another pill
that helps with my qi?

367
00:22:35,983 --> 00:22:37,654
I’ve told you.

368
00:22:37,655 --> 00:22:40,080
Those were supplements
to strengthen your body.

369
00:22:42,160 --> 00:22:46,638
When will people without
motivation like you start to catch up?

370
00:22:46,639 --> 00:22:48,000
Go away.

371
00:22:49,000 --> 00:22:50,040
Yes.

372
00:22:58,840 --> 00:23:01,560
Elder, you look troubled.

373
00:23:04,160 --> 00:23:07,199
According to
the result of the past few days,

374
00:23:07,200 --> 00:23:10,631
I don’t see a high chance
of winning from the aptitude shown

375
00:23:10,632 --> 00:23:12,680
by your disciple.

376
00:23:15,520 --> 00:23:17,399
Elder, please consider it.

377
00:23:17,400 --> 00:23:19,520
Do you still need my help?

378
00:23:22,960 --> 00:23:27,439
Xuanyuan Sect has been
declining for more than 20 years.

379
00:23:27,440 --> 00:23:29,199
A good opportunity is right in front.

380
00:23:29,200 --> 00:23:31,040
Just say the word.

381
00:23:33,360 --> 00:23:36,520
You just want to know
the whereabouts of the spirit keys.

382
00:23:37,800 --> 00:23:39,120
Fine.

383
00:23:39,640 --> 00:23:41,559
I will tell you.

384
00:23:41,560 --> 00:23:45,366
These four spirit keys
are mythological objects.

385
00:23:45,367 --> 00:23:50,471
Since the ancient times, they were
already guarded by the Four Sects

386
00:23:50,472 --> 00:23:55,254
and has been sealed by the Four Sects’
most treasured spirit item.

387
00:23:55,255 --> 00:23:56,754
Which Four Sects?

388
00:23:56,755 --> 00:23:58,022
Do tell.

389
00:23:58,023 --> 00:24:04,679
In this world, who else is capable
enough to secure the spirit keys?

390
00:24:04,680 --> 00:24:10,199
They are naturally, Donghai’s
Fuyu Island, Xiyang’s Lize Palace,

391
00:24:10,200 --> 00:24:12,160
Beihuang’s Dianjinggu

392
00:24:12,880 --> 00:24:14,360
and...

393
00:24:15,880 --> 00:24:18,679
And this place.

394
00:24:18,680 --> 00:24:20,760
Zhongyuan’s Shaoyang Sect.

395
00:24:22,671 --> 00:24:24,560
I see.

396
00:24:26,919 --> 00:24:30,319
Lize Palace’s Dragon Seal,
Fuyu Island’s Moon Blade

397
00:24:30,320 --> 00:24:34,119
and Dianjinggu’s Seven Star Disc
are known by everyone.

398
00:24:34,120 --> 00:24:36,880
I’ve never heard that Shaoyang Sect

399
00:24:37,712 --> 00:24:39,600
has a mythological object of their own.

400
00:24:40,240 --> 00:24:45,159
How can an outsider
tell you more about Shaoyang Sect?

401
00:24:45,160 --> 00:24:47,999
I’ve told you what I know.

402
00:24:48,000 --> 00:24:51,160
Please keep your promise

403
00:24:51,720 --> 00:24:54,620
and give these pills to me.

404
00:25:01,663 --> 00:25:04,080
I was just randomly asking.

405
00:25:08,280 --> 00:25:11,559
From now on, our deal ends here.

406
00:25:11,560 --> 00:25:14,160
We have no more connections. Farewell.

407
00:25:15,240 --> 00:25:16,920
Shaoyang Sect?

408
00:25:17,750 --> 00:25:21,320
Don’t tell me,
the secret ground hides the spirit key?

409
00:25:21,895 --> 00:25:23,822
Time flies by quickly.

410
00:25:23,823 --> 00:25:26,840
We are halfway through the Flower Session.

411
00:25:27,519 --> 00:25:29,039
I’m angry now that you mention it.

412
00:25:29,040 --> 00:25:31,031
Wu Tong is still in this tournament.

413
00:25:31,032 --> 00:25:33,119
But Si Feng will fight him tomorrow.

414
00:25:33,120 --> 00:25:36,106
Si Feng, you have to give him
an utter defeat.

415
00:25:36,719 --> 00:25:40,119
That’s because Si Feng is great.
Why are you feeling proud?

416
00:25:40,120 --> 00:25:42,062
Am I only allowed to be
embarrassed because you lost to Wu Tong

417
00:25:42,063 --> 00:25:43,501
but can’t feel proud at all?

418
00:25:43,502 --> 00:25:46,919
I lost because Wu Tong cheated, alright?

419
00:25:46,920 --> 00:25:48,639
I don’t want to care about you.

420
00:25:48,640 --> 00:25:50,800
You think I want to care about you?

421
00:25:52,560 --> 00:25:53,844
I’m leaving!

422
00:25:54,680 --> 00:25:56,160
Fine.

423
00:25:57,840 --> 00:26:00,600
Both of them are like that.

424
00:26:03,799 --> 00:26:05,519
What’s wrong, Si Feng?

425
00:26:05,520 --> 00:26:08,600
Why do you look unhappy?

426
00:26:09,480 --> 00:26:13,085
I am thinking that time really flies by.

427
00:26:13,086 --> 00:26:15,373
Once the Flower Session ends,

428
00:26:15,374 --> 00:26:18,013
I have to go back
to Lize Palace with my master.

429
00:26:18,014 --> 00:26:19,398
Yes.

430
00:26:19,399 --> 00:26:23,519
You have to go back
after the Flower Session.

431
00:26:23,520 --> 00:26:25,600
Can we still meet again?

432
00:26:29,680 --> 00:26:30,880
Yes.

433
00:26:31,400 --> 00:26:33,079
We will meet again.

434
00:26:33,080 --> 00:26:34,680
We will definitely meet

435
00:26:35,360 --> 00:26:36,800
no matter how hard it is.

436
00:26:37,800 --> 00:26:39,000
Xuan Ji.

437
00:26:40,879 --> 00:26:42,486
Just don’t forget me.

438
00:26:42,487 --> 00:26:44,680
I will definitely not forget about you.

439
00:26:45,240 --> 00:26:46,799
Si Feng, do you know?

440
00:26:46,800 --> 00:26:49,958
Everyone has been saying
I’m weird since I was young.

441
00:26:49,959 --> 00:26:52,398
No one wanted to be my friend.

442
00:26:52,399 --> 00:26:54,718
Besides Ling Long and Sixth Senior,

443
00:26:54,719 --> 00:26:56,960
you are the first friend that I made.

444
00:27:01,222 --> 00:27:03,120
You are weird indeed

445
00:27:03,640 --> 00:27:05,320
but I don’t care.

446
00:27:06,703 --> 00:27:08,158
Oh.

447
00:27:08,159 --> 00:27:11,159
I have a rare treasure here.

448
00:27:11,160 --> 00:27:14,646
It allows communication
with people from far away.

449
00:27:14,647 --> 00:27:16,000
Really?

450
00:27:24,800 --> 00:27:26,720
Where’s my silver hairpin?

451
00:27:39,720 --> 00:27:42,240
Why can’t we find it anywhere?

452
00:27:43,680 --> 00:27:45,381
It’s my fault.

453
00:27:45,382 --> 00:27:48,760
If it wasn’t to punish Wu Tong,

454
00:27:49,360 --> 00:27:53,359
you wouldn’t lose
the hairpin that your mother left you.

455
00:27:53,360 --> 00:27:54,920
It’s not your fault.

456
00:27:59,800 --> 00:28:01,240
It’s bad.

457
00:28:05,240 --> 00:28:07,320
Wu Tong has disappeared.

458
00:28:16,680 --> 00:28:19,719
Even if you attack from my back,
you won’t do anything to me.

459
00:28:19,720 --> 00:28:22,118
Don’t you think I learnt that from you?

460
00:28:22,119 --> 00:28:23,598
You hurt someone else first.

461
00:28:23,599 --> 00:28:26,159
We just want you
to repent on your mistakes.

462
00:28:26,160 --> 00:28:28,198
You don’t have to explain.

463
00:28:28,199 --> 00:28:30,526
He almost hurt Min Yan and Xuan Ji.

464
00:28:30,527 --> 00:28:33,646
Since you’ve been trapped for the night,
and has escaped now.

465
00:28:33,647 --> 00:28:36,319
This issue comes to an end.

466
00:28:36,320 --> 00:28:37,840
An end?

467
00:28:39,039 --> 00:28:41,335
I’ve never been embarrassed
to this extent.

468
00:28:41,336 --> 00:28:42,686
Do you think I’ll forget about it?

469
00:28:42,687 --> 00:28:44,760
You think I’m easily bullied?

470
00:28:45,503 --> 00:28:47,599
What do you want?

471
00:28:47,600 --> 00:28:50,640
I want you to kneel down,
and apologise to me.

472
00:28:51,520 --> 00:28:53,199
- You...
- Let’s go.

473
00:28:53,200 --> 00:28:54,360
Wait.

474
00:29:00,680 --> 00:29:02,679
- It’s with you.
- Xuan Ji.

475
00:29:02,680 --> 00:29:05,279
- It might be a trap.
- But he...

476
00:29:05,280 --> 00:29:08,120
When did you start
to care about Chu Xuan Ji’s safety?

477
00:29:08,800 --> 00:29:11,599
You don’t even want
the item your mother left you?

478
00:29:11,600 --> 00:29:14,919
I remember that falling in love
is not allowed in Lize Palace.

479
00:29:14,920 --> 00:29:16,679
You’ve broken the Palace’s rules.

480
00:29:16,680 --> 00:29:19,213
I will expose you. I want you to suffer.

481
00:29:19,214 --> 00:29:20,958
Si Feng, what is he talking about?

482
00:29:20,959 --> 00:29:24,600
I’m telling you. If you break Si
Feng’s item, I won’t forgive you.

483
00:29:25,600 --> 00:29:28,559
The second young lady of Shaoyang
looks foolish usually

484
00:29:28,560 --> 00:29:31,079
but you will get angry
because of Yu Si Feng?

485
00:29:31,080 --> 00:29:34,160
When did Lize Palace
and Shaoyang Sect got so close?

486
00:29:34,960 --> 00:29:37,774
I can do what I want with my friends.

487
00:29:37,775 --> 00:29:39,600
Return the hairpin to us.

488
00:29:42,024 --> 00:29:43,679
You want this?

489
00:29:43,680 --> 00:29:44,799
Sure.

490
00:29:44,800 --> 00:29:47,040
- Ask him to kneel down and beg me.
- You...

491
00:29:51,000 --> 00:29:52,359
Si Feng.

492
00:29:52,360 --> 00:29:55,879
You are just angry at
me for trapping you.

493
00:29:55,880 --> 00:29:57,640
Since you want to vent your anger,

494
00:29:58,647 --> 00:30:00,679
return the hairpin to me.

495
00:30:00,680 --> 00:30:04,000
You can beat me up
and I will never fight back.

496
00:30:06,520 --> 00:30:08,150
You will not fight back no matter what?

497
00:30:08,151 --> 00:30:11,239
It sounds appealing... but no.

498
00:30:11,240 --> 00:30:12,941
I have to waste my strength
to beat you up.

499
00:30:12,942 --> 00:30:16,280
I want you to kneel down and beg me.

500
00:30:18,631 --> 00:30:19,982
You...

501
00:30:19,983 --> 00:30:22,040
Return the hairpin to us.

502
00:30:28,480 --> 00:30:31,774
- Wu Tong, let me go.
- I am running out of patience.

503
00:30:31,775 --> 00:30:33,167
I will count to three.

504
00:30:33,168 --> 00:30:34,999
If you don’t kneel down,

505
00:30:35,000 --> 00:30:37,974
you won’t even save the girl’s face
let alone this hairpin.

506
00:30:37,975 --> 00:30:39,240
Wu Tong!

507
00:30:40,120 --> 00:30:42,279
Don’t act recklessly.

508
00:30:42,280 --> 00:30:43,919
- One.
- Wu Tong.

509
00:30:43,920 --> 00:30:45,919
I am the cause of this.

510
00:30:45,920 --> 00:30:47,559
Return the hairpin to Si Feng.

511
00:30:47,560 --> 00:30:50,199
You can scratch my face.

512
00:30:50,200 --> 00:30:52,360
- Two.
- Fine.

513
00:30:55,960 --> 00:30:57,799
- I’ll kneel.
- No!

514
00:30:57,800 --> 00:30:59,120
Shut up!

515
00:31:01,920 --> 00:31:06,919
I never thought this day will come
to Lize Palace’s genius disciple.

516
00:31:06,920 --> 00:31:09,839
I really want everyone to witness this.

517
00:31:09,840 --> 00:31:10,960
Kneel!

518
00:31:14,800 --> 00:31:16,080
Si Feng.

519
00:31:17,280 --> 00:31:18,600
No.

520
00:31:20,623 --> 00:31:21,920
No.

521
00:31:25,960 --> 00:31:27,400
Si Feng!

522
00:31:28,360 --> 00:31:29,800
Si Feng.

523
00:31:32,040 --> 00:31:33,440
No.

524
00:31:35,280 --> 00:31:37,600
Si Feng! No!

525
00:31:39,584 --> 00:31:41,068
Si Feng!

526
00:31:55,240 --> 00:31:56,360
Let’s go.

527
00:32:02,280 --> 00:32:03,959
Chu Xuan Ji. Yu Si Feng.

528
00:32:03,960 --> 00:32:05,560
Just you wait!

529
00:32:13,840 --> 00:32:14,959
Xuan Ji.

530
00:32:14,960 --> 00:32:18,159
This is the way you think of
to steal the hairpin?

531
00:32:18,160 --> 00:32:21,280
No one will notice us
if we dressed like this.

532
00:32:22,560 --> 00:32:23,959
Senior.

533
00:32:23,960 --> 00:32:25,440
Which way to the bath?

534
00:32:26,680 --> 00:32:28,519
Walk that way from here.

535
00:32:28,520 --> 00:32:31,280
- Look. It’s there.
- Be quiet.

536
00:32:31,281 --> 00:32:34,430
Xuan Ji, later you will sweep the floor,
and block Wu Tong’s vision.

537
00:32:34,431 --> 00:32:37,199
Leave the rest to me.
I will get the hairpin.

538
00:32:37,200 --> 00:32:38,919
- But I...
- You can’t cast any spells

539
00:32:38,920 --> 00:32:39,999
and my skills are better than you.

540
00:32:40,000 --> 00:32:41,200
Listen to me.

541
00:32:42,920 --> 00:32:44,320
Thank you, senior.

542
00:32:45,639 --> 00:32:47,760
He is leaving. Let’s follow him.

543
00:33:05,984 --> 00:33:07,179
- What’s wrong?
- Xuan Ji.

544
00:33:07,180 --> 00:33:08,614
This is the bathhouse for male disciples.

545
00:33:08,615 --> 00:33:10,720
Everyone is naked inside.

546
00:33:11,800 --> 00:33:14,319
Of course they have to
be naked to take a bath.

547
00:33:14,320 --> 00:33:16,879
Girls cannot see their naked body.

548
00:33:16,880 --> 00:33:18,639
Why is that?

549
00:33:18,640 --> 00:33:20,080
That...

550
00:33:20,829 --> 00:33:23,959
It’s because male and female
are different.

551
00:33:23,960 --> 00:33:25,399
Do you know that?

552
00:33:25,400 --> 00:33:28,807
It’s bad if word got out
that we went into the male bath.

553
00:33:28,808 --> 00:33:30,433
Why don’t we forget about it?

554
00:33:30,434 --> 00:33:31,679
It’s just a hairpin.

555
00:33:31,680 --> 00:33:33,839
Can we give Si Feng another one?

556
00:33:33,840 --> 00:33:35,039
That won’t do.

557
00:33:35,040 --> 00:33:36,735
Ling Long, do you know that
this hairpin

558
00:33:36,736 --> 00:33:38,519
is the only thing
given to Si Feng by his mother?

559
00:33:38,520 --> 00:33:40,486
It’s very important to him.
I must get it back.

560
00:33:40,487 --> 00:33:42,720
- Wait here. I’ll go.
- No.

561
00:33:43,440 --> 00:33:44,960
Wait here.

562
00:34:02,240 --> 00:34:04,239
- This place is so big.
- Yes.

563
00:34:04,240 --> 00:34:06,399
It must be so comfortable to bath here.

564
00:34:06,400 --> 00:34:09,112
After an arduous journey,
we have to take a nice bath today.

565
00:34:09,113 --> 00:34:10,319
Yes. I’ll be going first.

566
00:34:10,320 --> 00:34:11,440
Alright.

567
00:34:12,480 --> 00:34:15,040
Brother. Get me a towel.

568
00:35:04,727 --> 00:35:05,920
Hey!

569
00:35:06,880 --> 00:35:08,960
What are you doing?

570
00:35:10,480 --> 00:35:12,537
What a comfortable bath.

571
00:35:12,538 --> 00:35:14,400
I have to get a nice sleep.

572
00:35:45,480 --> 00:35:47,159
Chu Ling Long?

573
00:35:47,160 --> 00:35:48,440
It’s you.

574
00:35:49,280 --> 00:35:50,720
Hand it over.

575
00:35:58,680 --> 00:35:59,869
Stop pretending.

576
00:35:59,870 --> 00:36:02,199
Didn’t you enjoy yourself
at the male bathhouse?

577
00:36:02,200 --> 00:36:04,205
Who did you say
went into the male bathhouse?

578
00:36:04,206 --> 00:36:05,960
Shameless rascal!

579
00:36:15,840 --> 00:36:18,719
Luckily, I still have
my mother’s portrait.

580
00:36:18,720 --> 00:36:20,960
I have to remember how she looks.

581
00:36:26,880 --> 00:36:29,158
Silver Snake, don’t worry.

582
00:36:29,159 --> 00:36:31,839
I will get back the silver hairpin.

583
00:36:31,840 --> 00:36:33,760
Si Feng.

584
00:36:34,360 --> 00:36:35,525
Si Feng.

585
00:36:35,526 --> 00:36:36,760
Look.

586
00:36:38,935 --> 00:36:41,879
Why is your leg injured?

587
00:36:41,880 --> 00:36:43,600
Here. Sit down.

588
00:36:52,560 --> 00:36:55,319
Where did you get this injury?

589
00:36:55,320 --> 00:36:58,800
You got hurt because
you went to retrieve my silver hairpin?

590
00:36:59,400 --> 00:37:01,879
It’s fine. I can’t feel pain anyway.

591
00:37:01,880 --> 00:37:05,440
Most importantly,
I got back the treasure your mum left you.

592
00:37:18,480 --> 00:37:20,280
Si Feng, what are you looking at?

593
00:37:21,760 --> 00:37:23,440
Let me put some medicine.

594
00:37:24,840 --> 00:37:27,640
It’s fine. I don’t feel pain.

595
00:37:37,080 --> 00:37:40,359
Roll up your pants.

596
00:37:40,360 --> 00:37:45,280
Si Feng, why are you stammering?

597
00:37:46,240 --> 00:37:48,640
Roll up your pants
so I can apply medicine.

598
00:37:55,040 --> 00:37:58,440
Stop saying that you don’t feel pain,
and you are fine.

599
00:37:59,000 --> 00:38:00,559
You are bleeding.

600
00:38:00,560 --> 00:38:05,760
Although you don’t feel pain,
your body will still know it.

601
00:38:07,640 --> 00:38:09,101
Also, that Wu Tong

602
00:38:09,920 --> 00:38:11,374
is petty.

603
00:38:11,375 --> 00:38:13,160
You have to avoid him.

604
00:38:13,800 --> 00:38:15,080
Okay.

605
00:38:16,040 --> 00:38:17,280
Oh.

606
00:38:18,040 --> 00:38:20,254
How did you find this silver hairpin?

607
00:38:20,255 --> 00:38:22,640
Why are you dressed like this?

608
00:38:24,040 --> 00:38:28,360
I am smart.
I took it when Wu Tong was taking a bath.

609
00:38:29,160 --> 00:38:32,400
What? You went to the male bathhouse?

610
00:38:33,040 --> 00:38:35,996
How can a girl
go inside the male bathhouse?

611
00:38:37,200 --> 00:38:40,919
But the best time to steal it
was when Wu Tong was taking a bath.

612
00:38:40,920 --> 00:38:42,916
Your leg is injured. Sit down.

613
00:38:46,480 --> 00:38:49,719
Let me ask you. What did you see?

614
00:38:49,720 --> 00:38:51,079
I didn’t see anything.

615
00:38:51,080 --> 00:38:54,320
I only saw many disciples
running around naked.

616
00:38:55,671 --> 00:38:57,239
Do you know?

617
00:38:57,240 --> 00:39:00,839
It’s bad for a girl
if word of this got out?

618
00:39:00,840 --> 00:39:02,199
I... But...

619
00:39:02,200 --> 00:39:04,182
I saw you taking a bath before.

620
00:39:04,183 --> 00:39:06,160
There was nothing bad about it.

621
00:39:06,720 --> 00:39:08,160
I was bad.

622
00:39:09,360 --> 00:39:12,079
I mean, I’m different from other people.

623
00:39:12,080 --> 00:39:14,159
If you meet someone
trying to cause trouble,

624
00:39:14,160 --> 00:39:17,479
they will spread the news,
and exaggerate it.

625
00:39:17,480 --> 00:39:19,440
It will be bad for you.

626
00:39:20,480 --> 00:39:25,158
But, before I went in,
Ling Long told me the same thing.

627
00:39:25,159 --> 00:39:28,999
She said it’s bad and ran away.

628
00:39:29,000 --> 00:39:31,760
But, Si Feng, what is feeling shy?

629
00:39:37,040 --> 00:39:38,400
Roll them up.

630
00:39:47,280 --> 00:39:50,374
Feeling shy is to feel embarrassed.

631
00:39:50,375 --> 00:39:51,920
Feeling ashamed.

632
00:39:52,640 --> 00:39:55,440
Men and women are different.

633
00:39:55,960 --> 00:39:56,967
They will shy

634
00:39:56,968 --> 00:39:59,159
- if they touch each other.
- Men and women are different?

635
00:39:59,160 --> 00:40:04,679
So, you can never touch
another man in the future.

636
00:40:04,680 --> 00:40:08,280
Also, see no evil, touch no evil.

637
00:40:09,440 --> 00:40:13,600
Don’t touch a person
of another gender in the future.

638
00:40:14,280 --> 00:40:17,560
Si Feng, what you are doing...

639
00:40:19,720 --> 00:40:21,000
Si Feng.

640
00:40:21,520 --> 00:40:23,360
Are you feeling shy now?

641
00:40:32,560 --> 00:40:34,806
I’ll apply the medicine to you.

642
00:40:39,280 --> 00:40:40,760
Are you alright?

643
00:40:46,240 --> 00:40:48,239
I think Senior Xin has a higher chance.

644
00:40:48,240 --> 00:40:50,200
Lize Palace will surely win.

645
00:40:51,640 --> 00:40:52,827
Come here.

646
00:40:58,000 --> 00:41:00,599
Si Feng, why are you
sleeping so early tonight?

647
00:41:00,600 --> 00:41:01,880
Don’t move.

648
00:41:04,760 --> 00:41:06,879
Si Feng, are you hurt? Let me take a look.

649
00:41:06,880 --> 00:41:08,664
I’m fine. It’s minor.

650
00:41:09,440 --> 00:41:10,680
Then...

651
00:41:11,240 --> 00:41:13,350
Why are you sleeping with the robe on?

652
00:41:13,351 --> 00:41:16,280
- It’s cold.
- Let me cover the blanket for you.

653
00:41:19,000 --> 00:41:21,039
Si Feng, what’s the meaning of this?

654
00:41:21,040 --> 00:41:23,461
I’m going to sleep.
The lights were too bright.

655
00:41:23,462 --> 00:41:25,758
That’s it. You are the palace lord’s
top disciple.

656
00:41:25,759 --> 00:41:29,359
You can do anything you want
without caring about others.

657
00:41:29,360 --> 00:41:31,158
You are wrong.

658
00:41:31,159 --> 00:41:34,799
This top disciple
does care a lot for someone else.

659
00:41:34,800 --> 00:41:38,039
He only wanted to
be friends with some outsiders.

660
00:41:38,040 --> 00:41:41,534
I heard he even tried to help
the two girls from Shaoyang Sect.

661
00:41:41,535 --> 00:41:42,919
He did it publicly.

662
00:41:42,920 --> 00:41:45,959
I’m sure he had already
forgotten all about the palace rules.

663
00:41:45,960 --> 00:41:47,879
You are right. Seems like Si Feng

664
00:41:47,880 --> 00:41:50,079
is not planning to become
Lize Palace’s palace lord in the future

665
00:41:50,080 --> 00:41:53,240
but to stay in Shaoyang Sect,
and become their son-in-law.

666
00:41:53,920 --> 00:41:56,079
That’s enough. Stop talking.

667
00:41:56,080 --> 00:41:57,479
We have important work tomorrow.

668
00:41:57,480 --> 00:41:58,920
Rest early.

669
00:42:20,080 --> 00:42:21,759
What are you doing?

670
00:42:21,760 --> 00:42:25,320
Silver Snake stole my hair accessory.

671
00:42:26,480 --> 00:42:27,760
Don’t move.

672
00:42:28,720 --> 00:42:30,000
Take your hands off.

673
00:42:46,280 --> 00:42:47,759
Hao Chen.

674
00:42:47,760 --> 00:42:51,639
Among the young disciples
of Shaoyang Sect,

675
00:42:51,640 --> 00:42:53,720
I have the highest hope in you.

676
00:42:54,520 --> 00:42:56,158
Thank you, sect leader.

677
00:42:56,159 --> 00:42:57,822
Shaoyang Sect’s ancestors taught us

678
00:42:57,823 --> 00:42:59,254
the importance of the secret ground.

679
00:42:59,255 --> 00:43:00,719
It can never be broken into.

680
00:43:00,720 --> 00:43:03,686
Since Xuyang Peak
was given the responsibility to guard it,

681
00:43:03,687 --> 00:43:06,440
we will guard the safety
of the secret ground with our life.
